{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2018/03/ffmpeg-video-concat","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7efc5d08-117a-5bd3-9aef-384ec6b56083","html":"<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#0-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">0. 前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%89%AA%E5%88%87\">视频剪切</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6\">视频合并</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"0-前言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#0-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"0 前言 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>0. 前言</h1>\n<p>录了个视频，当中有大段的空档，于是想剪切掉中间的一段，这里记录下做法。</p>\n<h1 id=\"视频剪切\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%89%AA%E5%88%87\" aria-label=\"视频剪切 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>视频剪切</h1>\n<p>原视频大致是这么一个段落划分：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">~/Downloads/noname.mov\n\n00:00:00     00:01:05            00:02:08\n需要的第一部分     |     中间的空档      |      需要的第二部分</code></pre></div>\n<p>剪切的操作说明：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 从00秒开始裁剪到00+30=30秒结束，总共30秒的视频</span>\n    \n$ ffmpeg -ss 00:00:00 -t 00:00:30 -i test.mp4 -vcodec copy -acodec copy output.mp4\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># -ss 指定从什么时间开始</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># -t 指定需要截取多长时间</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># -i 指定输入文件</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>先把视频剪成两段：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ ffmpeg -ss 00:00:00 -t 00:01:05 -i ~/Downloads/noname.mov -vcodec copy -acodec copy ~/Downloads/cut2.mov    \n$ ffmpeg -ss 00:02:08 -t 01:00:00 -i ~/Downloads/noname.mov -vcodec copy -acodec copy ~/Downloads/cut2.mov</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"视频合并\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6\" aria-label=\"视频合并 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>视频合并</h1>\n<p>然后合并起来：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> ~/Downloads \n$ <span class=\"token function\">touch</span> ./list.txt\n$ <span class=\"token function\">vim</span> ./list.txt\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># file</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">file</span> ./cut1.mov\n<span class=\"token function\">file</span> ./cut2.mov\n\nffmpeg -f concat -safe <span class=\"token number\">0</span> -i ./list.txt -c copy ./concat.mov</code></pre></div>\n<p>完成。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>EOF</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2018/03/ffmpeg-video-concat","tagSlugs":["/tag/ffmpeg/","/tag/video/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-03-02T02:01:22.000Z","description":"","tags":["FFMPEG","Video"],"title":"ffmpeg视频剪切超简单教程","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/7e722e026a41a08a8f9a1cc76782dd27/default-social-image.jpg"}}},"allFile":{"totalCount":0,"nodes":[]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2018/03/ffmpeg-video-concat","gallery":"media/posts/2018/03/ffmpeg-video-concat/gallery"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}